high_descs: Turn and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the plant.
With the knife in turn and go to the island counter on the side where the lettuce is.
Slice half the lettuce on the right side with the knife.
With the knife in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the third shelf in front of the tomato. Shut the fridge.
Turn and go to the island counter where the lettuce is on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the middle.
With the slice of lettuce in hand turn and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge with lettuce in other hand.  Place lettuce to the left of the tomato behind the knife on the second shelf.  Close fridge. Open fridge and grab the lettuce that is on the second shelf
With the lettuce in your hand turn and go to the blue recycle bin that is to the left of the counter with the coffee pot on it.
Place the lettuce in to the blue recycle bin.
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce to put in fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left, move to the island, near the lettuce.
Slice the lettuce on the island.
Turn right, move to the front of the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn right, move to the island, near the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the island.
Turn right, move to the front of the refrigerator.
Put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the end of the counter at the blue bin.
Put the slice of lettuce in the blue bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of lettuce in the blue bin.

high_descs: Turn left and move to stand in front of the counter to the right of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the sharp knife from the counter.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, then take a right to stand at the end of the kitchen island.
Use the knife to slice the head of lettuce.
Turn right and move to the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge on the shelf next to the tomato.
Turn right to move back around the end of the island.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the island.
Turn right and carry the lettuce to the fridge.
Place the lettuce on the shelf by the tomato, close the door, and then open the door and remove the lettuce after a few seconds.
Turn left and when you get to the counter, turn left again and continue to the blue trash bin in the corner.
Place the lettuce in the blue trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a slice of cold lettuce.
